{"tid":706571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"縱火狂燒18架電單車 對面係將軍澳警署","createTime":"2018-06-18T04:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T04:15:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f68f2ec10f4b1976303e60b941a0811ac4c9fc76","tid":706571,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:12:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20424145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424145&d=PG4Oxvt61KFSqZ%2F8SnozV3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9342b3e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20424145&h=556affa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20424145</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n縱火狂燒18架電單車<br />\n對面係將軍澳警署<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】將軍澳敬賢里將軍澳警署對面，停在路邊的電單車凌晨突然起火，昨晨1時35分，警員巡經上址發現及通知消防。消防員到場開喉將火救熄，共有18輛電單車燒毀，大部份燒成廢鐵。消防在其中一輛電單車發現助燃劑，調查火警起因有可疑，交由警方跟進。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【港古佬】扒龍舟五大禁忌　女人點解唔扒得？<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n三父子同人嘈　中伏被電筒扑傷頭"},{"pid":"27db01582ed4ace51bd67f0c514736397c65cb3e","tid":706571,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"阿sir訓覺<br />\n唔洗你教"}]}